Contents: @everyone Hey everyone! I am currently trying to schedule another cricket game against the Blaine team. We are trying to find a time that works for everyone. Could you please fill out this form with the times that you are available for a cricket match? (It could be with time intervals  like "any time June 20-July 6th" or with specific dates). https://forms.gle/7321MKH8TLWvNEdX7
Also, please make sure to get your waivers turned in! Here's the Google form link: https://forms.gle/x4qWgg3NA7gvZfgZ8

@everyone This is a reminder that the game today starts at 5:30! Plan to be there a bit earlier. Also, since we are playing in Bryn Mawr Meadows Park in Minneapolis, plan for there to be a bit of traffic. Use Google Maps to make your timing estimates.
If we get rained on (hopefully not), we will definitely set up another time to play.
